<p>The short film shows the UK and US heads eating fried chicken in the hot room together before the Russian premier enters accompanied by two blondes and attacks.</p>

<p>Their towels drop during the fight to reveal their full puppet anatomies at the end of the jawdropping trailer.</p>

<p>A naked sauna room Kung-fu fight between Boris Johnson, Donald Trump and Vladimir Putin provides the shocking centrepiece of a trailer hearalding the return of puppet satire Spitting Image</p>

